# AI Agent Skills Framework (.mdc)

This rule enforces strict architectural separation of visual style tokens, structural layouts, and dynamic behaviors inside web projects to prevent style leaks and agent task evasion.

## Core Requirements
1. **State Lock**: Every modification must follow stage-by-stage execution in `.pipeline_state.json`.
2. **CSS Decoupling**: No raw colors (hex, rgb, hsl) inside layout files or inline style attributes. Run verification:
   ```bash
   python scripts/pipeline_validator.py
3. Self-Healing: Run diagnostic healing up to 3 times upon runtime errors before requesting human help.

Full specifications and CLI compiler scripts can be found at: 
https://github.com/luoning/agent-skills
